      <MissionDesc>Encompass Housing's mission is to build communities that foster a sense of belonging while creating safety nets that provide support and stability. Our goal is to serve all who are experiencing a housing crisis, including homelessness and housing insecurity, providing support, tools, and resources for them to move forward and achieve safety and stability. Our approach is to create a comprehensive continuum of housing services and resources that attends to the unique needs of every situation, from chronically homeless seniors to families experiencing homelessness. We are actively developing transitional and permanent housing projects while preparing to rapidly scale our services to meet the growing needs in our community.</MissionDesc>
